1. Executive Summary

ELBOT is an institutional-grade, AI-enhanced hybrid trading intelligence system that blends human-like reasoning with algorithmic precision.
It can both analyze and execute trades across multiple crypto markets — combining quantitative technical indicators, macro-awareness, and institutional liquidity tracking to trade intelligently and safely.

ELBOT supports two primary modes:
	•	🟢 AutoTrade: Fully automated order execution.
	•	⚪ ManualTrade: Human confirmation mode with full reasoning and signal transparency.

Its purpose: act as a disciplined, unemotional trader that flows with institutional liquidity, never against it.

