3. System Overview

Flow Diagram

TradingView → Flask API → TA Engine → Liquidity Intelligence → 
OpenAI Reasoning → Decision Fusion → Execution Engine → Alerts

Primary Layers
	1.	Data Layer — market feeds, liquidity data, macro inputs.
	2.	Indicator Engine — EMA, RSI, MACD, ATR, HMA, VWAP, CVD.
	3.	AI Reasoning Layer — human-style logic (OpenAI GPT-5).
	4.	Liquidity Intelligence — detects traps, walls, and sweeps.
	5.	Decision Fusion Engine — merges TA + AI + liquidity for final bias.
	6.	Execution Layer — handles spot/futures trades across venues.
	7.	Risk Controls & Alerts — Telegram, Pushover, Dashboard.

