4. Technical Components

Indicator Engine
	•	Computes core TA indicators (EMA, RSI, MACD, ATR).
	•	Detects divergences, trend changes, and volatility spikes.

AI Reasoning Layer
	•	Uses OpenAI GPT-5 for narrative-style reasoning.
	•	Takes numeric signals as structured JSON input.
	•	Returns structured decision: bias, confidence, rationale.

Liquidity Intelligence
	•	Reads order books via ccxt.pro.
	•	Detects liquidity traps, fake walls, and institutional sweeps.
	•	Tracks “big-player” profiles by size and timing.

Decision Fusion Engine
	•	Weighs outputs from TA, Liquidity, and AI modules.
	•	Outputs unified bias and confidence score.

Execution Layer
	•	Connects to multiple exchanges (Coinbase, Binance, MEXC, OKX).
	•	Executes trades via ccxt.pro (market, limit, OCO).
	•	Supports both spot and futures orders.

