5. Institutional Liquidity Intelligence

Purpose

Identify when large players create liquidity traps or manipulation zones, so ELBOT can wait for confirmation before acting.

Detection Logic (Simplified)

if price_moves_to_wall and volume_spike and closes_back_inside:
    bias = "reverse"

Concepts

Term	Meaning
Wall	High concentration of resting orders.
Sweep	Price breaks through wall consuming liquidity.
Trap	Fake move designed to trigger stops before reversal.

Strategy
	•	Track bid/ask imbalance.
	•	Monitor sudden wall creation or deletion.
	•	Wait for sweep → rejection → confirmation.
	•	Only act after absorption — never pre-empt moves.

Philosophy: “Trade after manipulation, not during it.”

