6. OpenAI Human-Style Reasoning Layer

How It Works

ELBOT sends structured market snapshots to OpenAI:

{
  "symbol": "XRPUSDT",
  "trend": "sideways",
  "rsi": 42.3,
  "volume_spike": true,
  "wall_detected": "2.95",
  "macro_risk": false
}

Example Prompt

“You are a professional, unemotional trader. Given this data,
explain the market structure, likely outcome, and bias (LONG/SHORT/WAIT).
Return JSON with bias, confidence, reasoning.”

Example AI Output

{
  "bias": "WAIT",
  "confidence": 64,
  "reasoning": "Support defended at 2.95; confirmation needed above 3.00."
}

Integration

AI reasoning never executes trades — it advises.
The decision engine validates alignment between numeric indicators and reasoning output before acting.

